query:
SELECT
                COUNT(DISTINCT session_id) as total_sessions,
                SUM(request_count)::bigint as total_requests,
                COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) as unique_users
            FROM user_sessions
            WHERE started_at >= NOW() - ($1 || ' days')::INTERVAL
              AND is_bot = false
              AND is_scanner = false
              AND request_count > 0
